tps://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1692078075", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 58326, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075", "stars": 8550, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 543375, "username": "gdb", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/gdb", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3781/3cce/543375_mini.png?m=1689813188", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3781/3cce/543375_normal.png?m=1689813188", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3781/3cce/543375_large.png?m=1689813188", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3781/3cce/543375_xlarge.png?m=1689813188", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3781/3cce/543375_xlarge.png?m=1689813188", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3781/3cce/543375_xlarge.png?m=1689813188", "created": 1619089090, "last_modified": 1689813188}, "last_reply_by": "xinge666", "last_touched": 1692812392, "title": "请问 github 的两步验证（two-factor authentication）大家是怎么做的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/967533", "created": 1692753573, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近收到 github 发来的邮件，要求账户进行两步验证，如果不进行两步验证，那么 45 天之后好像访问受限制了。\r\n\r\n我登陆看了一下，可以使用 SMS authentication ，但是进去看了一下，里面没有中国大陆的手机可以选择，压根里面就没有 China 的选项，所以用不了。\r\n\r\n另外一种选项是：Setup authenticator app ，提示的方法是：Use an authenticator app or browser extension to scan 。 但是我用手机的 Firefox 浏览器的扫码功能试验了一下，无法扫码这个二维码。\r\n\r\n请问大家是如何进行两步验证的？\r\n\r\n谢谢！", "content_rendered": "<p>最近收到 github 发来的邮件，要求账户进行两步验证，如果不进行两步验证，那么 45 天之后好像访问受限制了。</p>\n<p>我登陆看了一下，可以使用 SMS authentication ，但是进去看了一下，里面没有中国大陆的手机可以选择，压根里面就没有 China 的选项，所以用不了。</p>\n<p>另外一种选项是：Setup authenticator app ，提示的方法是：Use an authenticator app or browser extension to scan 。 但是我用手机的 Firefox 浏览器的扫码功能试验了一下，无法扫码这个二维码。</p>\n<p>请问大家是如何进行两步验证的？</p>\n<p>谢谢！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1692753573, "replies": 117, "id": 967533}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 23176, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2676, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 422112, "username": "noobjalen", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/noobjalen", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/edbd6a8075d00d02e558ac211688cd03?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/edbd6a8075d00d02e558ac211688cd03?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/edbd6a8075d00d02e558ac211688cd03?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1560629252, "last_modified": 1685526799}, "last_reply_by": "klementina", "last_touched": 1692803412, "title": "咸鱼 PD 标准版两年订阅，咸鱼一堆 26 元一个出售", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/967529", "created": 1692752123, "deleted": 0, "content": "买了几个，续到 31 年了。", "content_rendered": "<p>买了几个，续到 31 年了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1692752123, "replies": 112, "id": 967529}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 209599,